                        <shortdesc>Install a <ph conkeyref="ProductNames/pe_long"/> agent to
                                                regularly pull configuration catalogs from a <ph
                                                  conkeyref="ProductNames/puppet"/> master, and
                                                apply them to your target <ph
                                                  conkeyref="ProductNames/linux"/> or <ph
                                                  conkeyref="ProductNames/windows"/> nodes. The
                                                agent maintains the node configuration you
                                                want.</shortdesc>
